lattice      fcc 4.4300
Lattice spacing in x,y,z = 4.4300000 4.4300000 4.4300000
region       box block 0 ${xx} 0 ${yy} 0 ${zz}
region       box block 0 20 0 ${yy} 0 ${zz}
region       box block 0 20 0 20 0 ${zz}
region       box block 0 20 0 20 0 20
create_box   1 box
